{"tid":1681211,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"不明氣體襲屯門　3歲女童頸背手出紅疹","createTime":"2019-10-29T09:23:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-29T09:39:10.000Z","uid":39464,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"bd9dbf8a8120f2b1bf7877bd7d4f5f56aaa5ffa4","tid":1681211,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T09:23:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20191029/photo/bkn-20191029160204413-1029_00822_001_01p.jpg?20191029165432\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20191029%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20191029160204413-1029_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20191029165432&h=8ff95637&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n屯門昨午(28日)受到不明氣體侵襲，有居民表示該氣味類似催淚氣體，非常刺鼻難聞，更有年僅3歲幼童疑受這些氣體影響，背、頸、手等出紅疹及痕癢。事隔一日，各政府部門仍未正面回應事件，多名地區人士直斥政府不負責，促盡快交代。<br />\n<br />\n屯門山景邨居民陳小姐昨午約4時到幼稚園接女兒放學，已感到空氣較平日刺鼻難聞，喉嚨感不適及有咳嗽。豈料回家不到半小時，3歲女兒皮膚即出現紅疹及發癢，陳猜測女兒是受不明氣體影響，即為女兒沖身及塗藥膏，女兒昨晚亦睡不好。陳未有帶女兒求醫，憂再出街會令傷患加劇。另有寵物店指有數十隻貓狗疑受影響不停嘔吐，有倉鼠死亡。<br />\n<br />\n多名地區人士及居民重申只想「求個明白」，但不滿警方昨晚發射多枚催淚彈及胡椒噴霧驅散街坊。若事件確與催淚氣體洩漏無關，警方更應交代。居民又不滿食衞局、教育局等連月來未有教導市民如何處理催淚彈的影響，斥政府不負責任。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20191029/mobile/bkn-20191029160204413-1029_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20191029%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20191029160204413-1029_00822_001.html&d=WC8zRIkQRph3x4hQUB%2Bsg4T2PPn%2Ft%2FQrHStoP3Eljfw%3D&h=c41fbc2d\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20191029/mobile/bkn-20191029160204413-1029_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"16fd9dc50a8c63da07a3cd20a7bbdc73787896a8","tid":1681211,"uid":291465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T09:24:27.000Z","msg":"黑警已經開始使用化武鎮壓平民<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c7bed9c41e2615a0564b7a29bb1dcf38400b931","tid":1681211,"uid":110743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T09:24:34.000Z","msg":"一定要追究 推"},{"pid":"c9300689faa44d87c3ff19e5a0e83c1545537a81","tid":1681211,"uid":160650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T09:29:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7b75f6fc50465bf0864b8527ea7fe1e3868fbf67","tid":1681211,"uid":160650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T09:30:11.000Z","msg":"推 追究班仆街狗<br />\n班狗係咪腦裝水"},{"pid":"c90f53a833e6a6396d0eb7d2e339b9eeb082ad64","tid":1681211,"uid":136893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T09:30:43.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">記唔記得7、8月既時候，臨有行動前一日既連登，係充滿住遊行路線、離開方法、行動目的地既街坊整既攻略、仲有各種各樣既行動資訊整合，所有行動都係至小早半個月搞，有D 活動更加係會根據其重要性去調配，例如我記得葵青區遊行係推遲左成個月的。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n反思行動及行動數量<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">（極緊急！！！）等我教大家點再引發群眾熱情<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1680895\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1680895</a></span></span>"},{"pid":"9e6329e0fe07d3d5a6d99512f8110c28aa135f82","tid":1681211,"uid":34990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T09:34:34.000Z","msg":"頭先睇記者會個媽媽好嬲，又唔知點算好"},{"pid":"6a5caa9c39d6c4b09d626fd7556d052f2eae5ee6","tid":1681211,"uid":50744,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T09:39:10.000Z","msg":"唔想有事可以唔住屯門<br />\n支持香港警察<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}